  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Requirement for open-heart (including emergency) surgical procedures requiring
             cardio-pulmonary bypass:

               -  Either:

                    -  Age ≥ 70 to &lt;80 with a Parsonnet Mortality Risk Score of ≥13 (poor risk); OR

                    -  Age ≥ 80
      </textblock>
